{"TopicId":155627,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"Updated Wheel Rigging Tutorial?","CreatedByName":"SasquatchM","CreatedById":11888,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-27T04:21:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SasquatchM","CreatedById":11888,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-27T04:21:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI finally took the time to go through some wheel tutorials only to discover that most of what is out there is not up to date. Does anyone know the location of some up-to-date tutorials?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-27T13:24:39Z\u0022 title=\u002201/27/2017 01:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by SasquatchM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SasquatchM","CreatedById":11888,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-28T00:31:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is the hierarchy I got importing\u00A0 one of Squad\u0027s wheels into Blender. Hope someone can find this useful\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/M8WFQRY.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022M8WFQRY.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-29T14:44:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi as wheels are still a dark art for many I hope you don\u0027t object if I share a few more Unity wheel images showing hierarchies, colliders etc ,\u00A0 all images are as exported to the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst the TR2L type\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022bQtmsss.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bQtmsss.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DzX5Scj.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/DzX5Scj.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022vmhCvVz.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vmhCvVz.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd the M1 type (which btw the squad version is broken and has the wrong hierarchy) below is the correct hierarchy for an M1 type, do not use the stock example\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PFsNxS1.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PFsNxS1.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UpFR6YA.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UpFR6YA.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UIRnQxR.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022625\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UIRnQxR.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}